 *French tip, glitter or art add extra

After your first session, you will receive a thumb drive with your photos on it, each session after that you will need to bring that thumb drive back so I can add the new months photos to it! On your final session you will receive a free 8x10!

name: 3D Natural Looking Eyebrows
blurb:
Professionally enhanced eyebrows frame your face, enhance your features, and provide a youthful “lift” to your eyes. As one of our most requested procedures, permanent eyebrows add shape, fullness, and symmetry that can take years off your appearance and save you untold hours in front of a mirror hassling with getting them "just right". We can blend single hair tattooing into existing brow hairs, matching to your hair color and growth pattern for a completely natural look. If starting from scratch, we will create a design [along with your help] that you will love and that looks great on you.    

Our most requested service is eyebrow tattooing, and we are the West Coast experts at creating the most real looking "3-D" brows possible. If you’re tired of spending time every day drawing on your eyebrows, or tired of worrying about them rubbing off as you live your life – we can help. 

Once we gain a good understanding of the shape and color you want, we work with you to develop a color palette tailored to blend with and complement your skin and hair color. Then, using a very precise application technique, we painstakingly create single hairs with the smallest tattoo needle available. Using multiple shades of pigment, then layering and highlighting, a three dimensional effect is achieved for the most natural looking brow possible. Truly, our results frequently go unnoticed because the brows look so real - even up close. If you don’t tell anyone that your eyebrows have been tattooed – no one will ever know!                         

Two sessions are almost always required to achieve optimal results, which are the brows we are know for - realistic, natural and having a "soft" appearance.

name: Areola/Nipple Tattoo Post-Surgery
blurb:
The art of restoring the appearance of areola and nipple tissue is oftentimes regarded as nothing short of a miracle for anyone that has undergone a mastectomy or other types of breast surgery. Our tattooing provides such natural looking results that even up close We can also apply pigment to add color or definition, or to give visual correction for size, shape, and symmetry.

We approach our areola/nipple work differently than most technicians - as if our tattooing is a work of art - basically an "oil painting". We have an artist's background - over 30+ years of painting with water colors, oils, and acrylics. Much as we would when we start on a canvas project, we create a large color palette of pigments that include lighter colors, mid tones, and dark shades. Using just 2 colors is the industry norm (a light and a dark), but we feel a broader palette gives us the ability to create a more detailed result with texture, depth, highlighting, and shadows. We apply the pigments over the course of typically 2-4 sessions, layering and varying the pigments for an end result that is astoundingly natural looking. We are extremely passionate about this service, and hope to a driving force in raising the industry bar for this kind of work.

Our areola restoration work is truly the icing on the cake for feeling complete, normal and beautiful. These pigmentation services include:

Areola-Nipple Complex Simulation - This procedure is for clients who have had breast reconstruction surgery. Pigment is implanted to create a realistic, three dimensional areola complex and nipple, and colors can be custom mixed to create shading that gives the illusion of protrusion and texture.
Color & Size Adjustment – Aesthetic corrections can be applied to help address size, shape, color, and symmetry. We can help you achieve a more balanced look, even coloring, and an overall aesthetically pleasing result following surgery. Patients with skin discoloration, lightly colored or faded tissue, or irregularities in color, shape, or size (i.e. too light/too small) can also benefit from re-pigmentation.
Since all permanent cosmetic procedures are considered to be a process, and generally more than one session is required to achieve desired results. Rarely, if ever, will results be perfect after just one pigment application, and most areola work requires 2-3 full treatments. As with all permanent color procedures, pigment color fades with time so touch-up maintenance may be required to keep your look vibrant and fresh.

name: No-Pain Eyeliner
blurb:
Gorgeously define your eyes with permanent eyeliner! You will love waking up looking great and continuing with that fresh look all day and into the night. Imagine life without strain or struggle to get your liner on straight, no more smears smudges or drips, and never worrying about sweat or tears causing makeup drips. It’s also the perfect solution for anyone with allergies, contact lens sensitivities, dexterity issues, vision problems, or a very active lifestyle. Quite literally, permanent eyeliner can instantly change your life for the better!

For many, permanent eyeliner gives the face a real “lift” and can take years off your appearance, as well as adding depth and definition. Shape, length, and strategic placement of the eyeliner can also help correct the appearance of certain eye shapes and facial asymmetry.

We offer a large selections of colors from which to choose, and we can also custom mix to meet your need. Dimensions of length and width varies depending on preference, from a very thin application placed in the lash line for a more natural look to a higher drama with thicker lines. Requests for extra thick-width eyeliner is quoted separately, as lid tissue can only tolerate a certain amount of trauma in a single sitting. Once critical mass is reached relative to tissue swelling, skin will no longer accept pigment. More often than not, achieving a very thick line requires two applications, in addition to the touch-up.

name: Scar Camouflage
blurb:
Scar camouflage, depositing flesh-colored pigments into skin or scar tissue, is also known as Corrective Pigment Camouflage (CPC). This is a very specialized area of paramedical tattooing, and very few technicians have the expertise or artistic eye to do it well. At Anew You Studio - we have both.

We are experts at creating near-perfect color blends to match skin tone with very natural looking results, as well as implanting pigments in such a way to closely match the appearance of surrounding tissue. Our CPC work helps restore coloring to tissue that has been compromised from events such as burns, trauma injury, surgery, acne, and other imperfections. 

After determining the best color "recipe", pigment is then carefully applied in varying techniques in order to simulate color and texture of the surrrounding tissue. The appearance of the treated area becomes much less noticeable, and we can also apply fine hair strokes or a “stubble effect to areas with permanent hair loss (such as beard growth) to achieve the most natural look possible. Great improvement can be achieved, but CPC cannot completely restore how the skin looked prior to injury, so expectations must be realistic.

name: SERVICES:
blurb: Yours Smoothly is a waxing parlor completely devoted to giving you your smoothest skin ever! Hate razor burn? Hate cutting your legs when you shave? Dread shaving almost every day? Don't want to waste your time in the shower with razors and shaving cream? THEN DON'T! Turn to waxing! It's easier to maintain and won't leave you with razor burn or stubby legs! Here's the lowdown: WAX The first time you get your legs waxed, it's possible you may still feel some stubblies. This is because all of your hairs are in a different growth cycle. The more you wax, the smoother they get! When the hair does grow back, it grows back less and it grows back so much softer! After so many waxes, the hair will stop growing altogether! Say good-bye to razors! Hate getting cold and then feeling like you need to go and shave yet again? Get a wax and you don't have to deal with that annoyance! Waxing lasts so much longer than shaving. No more shaving every couple days! Scared it's gonna hurt? I'm not gonna lie, there is some pain involved. How much depends solely on your pain tolerance. Dry skin also seems to be more painful for people so if you are dry, just use lotion regularly before the wax. BUT! Have no fear! I possess a numbing spray that will help dull the pain, especially helpful for those daring enough to get a bikini or my first timers! :) Prices are as follows: *eyebrow-7 *lip-5 *chin-5 *underarms-10 *half arm-10 (to elbow) *full arm-15 *bikini-25 *extended bikini-30 (inner thighs and to the beginning of the labia) *brazilian-35 (EVERYTHING) *half leg-20 (to knee) *full leg-25 (includes top of foot and toes if applicable) *chest-30 *back-30 PARAFFIN Tired of having dry, cracked, painful hands and feet? Turn to paraffin! Paraffin is not only for people looking for smooth, soft skin. Paraffin has many benefits, including those for older people. Paraffin is a form of heat therapy and is very beneficial for people with ailments such as arthritis, osteoarthritis, tendonitis, muscle and tendon pain and fibromyalgia. It can also soften hardened skin caused by scleroderma. It increases the skins elasticity and allows the skin to move more! Price: $12 per set (hands, feet, elbows, knees) **Price includes a hand facial before the paraffin and a moisturizer after** Yours Smoothly will offer a variety of homemade Sugar Scrubs, Lotions and Lip Balms. Prices will be up soon! Yours Smoothly will be by appointment only on Monday-Friday anytime from 5:30 pm-9:00 pm and then I'm by appointment only on Saturday all day from 10 am to 8 pm. Yours Smoothly accepts cash, Mastercard, Visa and Discover Card. Tips are always welcome!

name: Trigger Point Therapy
blurb: A trigger point is a tight area within muscle tissue that causes pain in other parts of the body. A trigger point in the back, for example, may produce referral pain in the neck. The neck, now acting as a satellite trigger point, may then cause pain in the head. The pain may be sharp and intense or a dull ache. Trigger point massage therapy is specifically designed to alleviate the source of the pain through cycles of isolated pressure and release. In this type of massage for trigger point therapy, the recipient actively participates through deep breathing as well as identifying the exact location and intensity of the discomfort. The results and benefits of trigger point massage are releasing constricted areas in the muscles thus alleviating pain. You can experience a significant decrease in pain after just one treatment. Receiving massage with trigger point therapy on a regular basis can help naturally manage pain and stress from chronic injuries.

name: Deep Tissue Massage
blurb: Deep tissue massage therapy is similar to Swedish massage, but the deeper pressure is beneficial in releasing chronic muscle tension. The focus is on the deepest layers of muscle tissue, tendons and fascia (the protective layer surrounding muscles, bones and joints).

name: Sports Massage
blurb: Sports massage therapy is geared toward athletes of every kind. The particulars of the sports massage technique are specific to the athlete's sport of choice. Focusing on areas of the body that are overused and stressed from repetitive and often aggressive movements. A sports massage can be used as a means to enhance pre-event preparation and reduce recovery time for maximum performance during training or after an event.

name: Swedish Massage
blurb: Swedish massage therapy is what often comes to mind when people most people think about a massage. One of the primary goals of the Swedish massage technique is to relax the entire body. This is accomplished by rubbing the muscles with long gliding strokes in the direction of blood returning to the heart. But Swedish massage therapy goes beyond relaxation. Swedish massage is exceptionally beneficial for increasing the level of oxygen in the blood, decreasing muscle toxins, improving  circulation and flexibility while easing tension.

name: Prenatal Massage
blurb: A prenatal massage is a healthy way to reduce stress and promote overall wellness. Massage relieves many of the normal discomforts experienced during pregnancy, such as backaches, stiff neck, leg cramps, headaches and swelling. Massages for pregnant women reduce stress on weight-bearing joints, encourages blood and lymph circulation, helps to relax nervous tension -- which aids in better sleep -- and can help relieve depression or anxiety caused by hormonal changes.

name: Cancellation Policy
blurb:
Cancellation Policy
We ask that you call us at least 24 hours in advance if you need to cancel your appointment. Should cancellation occur through no fault of Watson’s One Stop Barber and Beauty Salon less than 24-hours prior to the scheduled appointment time and Watson’s One Stop Barber and Beauty Salon is unable to fill the cancelled time, 50% of the service cost will be applied to the client's next visit.	

Late Arrivals
If you are more than 20 minutes late without contacting us, your appointment will be rescheduled. We firmly believe in the value of your time and make a conscience effort to avoid long waiting periods in the salon. If time is critical to your schedule on a particular day, please make us aware of your schedule when scheduling your appointment.	

Missed Appointments
In the event that you miss three consecutive appointments without contacting the salon, you will be unable to schedule future appointments. However, you may be considered as a walk-in.
	
Confirmation Calls
As a courtesy, we try to call and confirm your color appointments a business day prior to your appointment. However, if we are unable to call or reach you, please understand that it is your responsibility to remember your appointment dates and times to avoid late arrivals, missed appointments and the cancellation fee.	

Children Policy
As a courtesy to other salon guests, and in our efforts to offer a relaxed and professional atmosphere we ask that you are aware that it is your responsibility to watch your children at all times while in the salon.	

Returned Fees
Any returned fees from credit cards will be subject to a $25.00 returned card fee
	
Walk-Ins
We welcome walk-in customers, however if it is not convenient with our schedule you may have a waiting period or need to schedule an actual appointment.	

Fees
All fees for services rendered are expected upon completion of services. We will be more than happy to discuss all charges and fees. Considering that all services are individually priced, please request a total price prior to receiving services. If you should conclude that you are unable to pay for all your services, we will gladly reschedule your appointment. Please Note - Credit for salon services is not an option.

name: ORDERING INSTRUCTIONS
blurb:
1. Choose your wig design service from the menu & click BOOK. You'll receive an email confirmation and my "Fits Like A Glove Measuring instructions.

A $50 non-refundable deposit is due when your order appointment is booked. The balance is due when the design is complete.  Turnaround time is 14 days. Faster turnaround is available... 

7 day RUSH service add $75. 

3 day RUSH service add $100.

A 5% discount is offered for payments upfront.

2. Email your style inspiration pictures of the look you desire to designmywig@gmail.com

3. Send your hair to me for design services. My mailing address will be on the service deposit invoice.

Questions? Tap CALL or MESSAGE to reach me.

blurb:

Keratin Fusion Texture Control is an innovative salon service that instantly and permanently transforms coarse, curly, unruly hair to smooth, straight and manageable locks.  Keratin Fusion gently but effectively straightens the hair and simultaneously imparts pure keratin protein to both the interior and exterior of the hair shaft, leaving long-lasting shine and an incredibly smooth surface.

Does not include trim or haircut.

Mizani is a brand of ethnic hair care products designed exclusively to work together promoting healthy hair even if you choose to relax your texture and rock silky straight tresses. Using the complete mizani line from start to finish will ensure that the health of your hair and scalp are never compromised during the service, protecting your scalp from chemical burns and your relaxed ends form over processing. Yes, many people with say relaxers are damaging but when the appropriate steps are taken to prevent damage during the process the common complaints of dryness and breakage can be successfully avoided. Happy hair is manageable hair for you and your lifestyle! Use only the best to ensure the best results! name: Full braided sew in
blurb: Sew in extensions involve braiding the hair in a cornrowed pattern across the scalp and sewing the wefted track to the braid. This method is often healthy for the hair making it thicker and fuller due to the lack of contact with heat from straightening. This method is available to all ethnicities and hair types.

name: Full braidless sew in
blurb: This braidless sew in method involves using microtubes to create the lead in the natural hair. From there, the wefted track is sewn to the lead track creating a sleek, flat, very discrete look. This method works great for fine or relaxed hair. Especially recomemended for Caucasian hair.

name: Full hot fusion
blurb: Hot fusion is a form of strand by strand extensions using a hot tool and u-tipped extensions, fusing the extensions to the hair. This method of extension has a risk of damaging the hair if not removed properly. So our recommendation is to return for proper removal before re-installing.

name: Microlinks (Cold Fusion)
blurb: This price does not include the hair.  Microlinks are a form of strand by strand extensions that are attached by small links to the natural hair. There is low damage risk and easy removal. This method is more expensive but better for the hair.

name: Hair extension custom color
blurb: Our high quality virgin hair comes standard in blonde, brown, and natural dark brown color.  We offer custom coloring to match your natural hair to provide the most blended look possible.  Our custom colorist will achieve the look you are looking for.

name: Braided sew in Shampoo and Tighten

name: Corrective Hair Color
blurb: I can correct any nightmare color you may have on your hair, due to home color or because someone else colored it and did not do it correctly.  I take my time and do an in depth consultation of the color, what was used on it, the target goal you would like your color to be at, and correct the problem.  If it is any easy fix the price is cheaper, but most of the time it is a very time consuming process because I do intense conditioning treatments on your hair during and after the color correction.

name: Keratin Express Blowout

name: Chlorine hair treatments
blurb: This helps eliminate the chlorine residue from swimming which can cause discolor of your hair and make the hair feel dry and brittle.  It takes away the residue and leaves hair looking brighter, shinier, and feel healthier.

name: Morrocain Oil Dry Scalp treatment
blurb: This is a wonderful treatment if you suffer from dry scalp, it is also a very relaxing treatment.  You will notice a big difference after your first treatment.

name: Morrocain Oil Oily Scalp treatment
blurb: This is a great and relaxing treatment if you suffer from an oily scalp.  This treatment helps reduce the oil production in the scalp without over drying the scalp out.

name: Full Head Hair Extensions
blurb: If you need length, volume, or both I can help you achieve this with Hothead Extensions. I use a breakthrough new technology of hair extensions that does not damage and break off the hair. These extensions can be reused for up to 9 months with proper scheduled maintenance with me. Call today to set up your free consultation! I need to consult with you at least two weeks before you need the extensions put in please.

name: Hair Extension Consult
blurb: Free Hotheads Hair Extension consultation is required 2 weeks before hair extensions are put in.  Consultation includes in depth extension home maintenance instruction, matching extensions to hair color, determining desired volume and length of extensions, and the cost of the hair needed for the service. Payment for hair is required before I order hair, once hair is ordered payment is non refundable.  Hair extensions cannot be returned once ordered, once hair comes in it cannot leave the salon unless it is applied to the hair due to certification contract agreement with Hotheads,

name: *Eyelash extensions Full set
blurb:
Extend your lash to a fuller, longer and very natural looking. Water proof, weightless no more mascara. This type of lash extend your lash to a fuller, longer and very natural looking. Water proof, weightless no more mascara. Like your scalp hair, natural eyelashes grow and shed in a cycle, which is typically 60 days. 
People typically shed 1-5 lashes each day, depending on their individual growth cycles. The lash extension will remain in place until the natural lash on which it rests falls out. Refills are necessary to replenish the fallen hairs and maintain the look. The average client takes approximately 70 lashes per eye or 140 lashes depending on their eyelases.. ) They will last anywhere from 3 thru 8 weeks depending on individual lash cycle and maintenance. (approx. 120 min.)


NOTE: No eye makeup, no eye cream, and no caffeine before the appointment

name: Bridal Party Makeup Consultation
blurb:
Booking a makeup trial: Before your wedding day it's advisable to have a makeup trial first, This should take place a couple of weeks before your big day, although if you wish to have a trial sooner than this, then that's fine with me too. By this time, you should have some idea of how you will be wearing your hair, what accessories you have, the style of your dress & your color scheme. This will determine what colors and styles of makeup we are going to use. I will apply your makeup to see how you will look on the day itself, & to check if you are sensitive to any products. Any changes will be made until you are 100% happy. Everything will be documented so that on the day there is no stress or confusion to the final look, so you can just sit back & relax.

Keep note* all makeup will be removed after satisfied with final look. 
You have an option to keep your final makeup on for your night on the town for an additional fee of $20.

Self Esteem Mobile Salon & Spa offers South, West, Suburbs and Chicago-land premier on-site hair and make-up services. Hair and Make-up stylist affiliated with Self Esteem Mobile Salon & Spa strive to be the BEST in the industry and provide consistently superior service for all events. We will come to you, fully equipped with hair and make-up supplies. For whatever occasion, our team will bring out your inner beauty so you can shine on your big day! name: Paraffin Wax Treatments
blurb:
Paraffin Wax retains heat which increases the skin's circulation and opens pores. Due to the dense molecular structure of the paraffin wax, it sits heavily on the skin “sealing” in serums and moisturizers. The skin is softened, nourished and rejuvenated. It soothes aching joints and muscles due to increased blood flow, which reduces pain and stiffness. Paraffin wax treatments reduce fluid retention; thereby decreasing inflammation. Skin color improves giving it a natural glow. Beyond skin and medical advantages of paraffin treatments, the mind is also soothed. Healing troubling aches and pains is very calming.  

The areas treated are cleansed and exfoliated. Corrective serums and nourishing moisturizers are massaged into the areas. The warm paraffin wax is placed and covers the entire treatment area. Mitts and booties are placed on hands and feet. After 15-20 minutes the paraffin wax slides off easily and any remaining moisturizer is massaged in to finish off this fantastic treatment!

name: Super Hydration Steam Treatment
blurb:
Steam Treatment

Steam hair treatments are often recommended for people with dry and/or damaged hair. It is considered a great solution for African-American women, as this treatment is bound to make the hair easier to handle.

The steam hair treatment works as a deep conditioning treatment for your hair. Steam and heat are both used in order to improve the condition of your hair.

The aim of the steam hair treatment is to hydrate the hair by opening the hair cuticles. This way, moisture can penetrate the hair shaft. Thanks to this, your hair becomes stronger, softer and, most of all, healthier.

The steam and heat are both good for your scalp, as well. They increase blood circulation in your scalp, which helps with hair growth and prevents hair loss.

name: Consultation
blurb:
Kimberly is available for 30-minute consultations if you’d like to see the clinic, meet her and chat before a procedure. Keep in mind that she goes through this same extensive consultation prior to any procedure on the day of the procedure. If you are fairly certain that you want to get a procedure, you can skip the consultation and instead book an appointment, or call the office to answer questions instead of making two trips.

If you choose to book a consultation, they are informational only and do not include any makeup designing. The $75 reservation fee is applied as credit towards any service booked.

name: Camoflauge
blurb: The repigmentation of skin that has become discolored due to scarring or other complications.

blurb: The white scar that results from some surgeries, including augmentation, is blended with a matching color back into the areola.

The hair is then treated with a recommended scalp and/or hair treatment followed with a scalp massage and finished off with a new weave installation.

name: Vienna Eyelash Extentions
blurb:
Vienna Lash Extensions are individual lashes made of silk micro fiber that are curved to replicate a natural eyelash. They are applied to individual lashes one at a time, for a natural, elegant look to lengthen and add fullness to the existing lashes.

With proper application, Vienna Lash extensions look and feel completely real. Each application is customized to each client. The application is very relaxing with most clients falling asleep while having the lashes applied. With proper application and maintenance, Vienna Lash Extensions will remain in place until the natural lash on which it is applied falls out. This can be between 2 weeks and as long as 4 weeks or more. 

The cost of Vienna Lash application will vary depending on the look you want.

name: Fully Kissed
blurb:
Not for the shy or fainthearted. "Fully Kissed" offers a full face of makeup. This is a full to medium coverage with primer, foundation, brows, eyeshadow(s), blush, eyeliner, mascara, contouring, lip liner, and of course a lip color/ gloss. This look is finished off with a setting spray which last up to 5 hours. 

**Don't forget to upgrade your experience by adding on "Deluxe Kisses"**

name: Partially Kissed
blurb: For a more gentle approach. "Partially Kissed" offers a basic "natural" face of makeup. This is a medium to light coverage with primer, foundation, brows, blush, eyeliner, lip liner and a gloss. This look is lightly dusted with an HD finishing powder for oil control and to keep you looking as flawless but natural as possible. Think along the lines of a "barely there" makeup appearance.

name: Sun Kissed
blurb: Find your light! "Sun Kissed" offers a very basic "glowing" face of makeup. This is a medium coverage with primer, foundation, brows, mascara, bronzing, contouring and highlighting. This look is finalized with a highly moisturizing finishing spray that keeps your skin appearing youthful and full of light...even with an overcast on the most cloudy of days!

name: Color Kissed
blurb: Free party at it's finest! "Color Kissed" offers a basic face of makeup with a slight twist. This is a medium coverage with primer, foundation, brows, blush, eyeshadow(1), and lip color. A finishing spray is used to complete this look for that camera ready finish. Imagine... tasteful splashes of a color on your face!

name: Deluxe Kisses
blurb: Upgrade any look by adding on "Deluxe Kisses" which include a skincare treatment for makeup application, custom high quality lash extensions and 16 hour water resistant setting spray. Swimming on the first date? Not a problem(:

name: Glitter Kisses
blurb: Customize your look by adding on "Glitter Kisses" for a touch of glitter to your eyeshadow! It's like fairy dust on your eyelids! Simply MAGICAL(:

name: Secret Weapon
blurb:
Maybe you don't need a full face of makeup. "Secret Weapon" provides the opportunity to just get those lashes & brows kissed. With simple strip lashes and a brow touch up who's to say you have on anything at all?

**Upgrade this service by adding on Deluxe Kisses**

name: Tinted Kisses
blurb: Upgrade your look by adding on "Tinted Kisses" to take that plain one color lip to an exciting ombre lip; maybe even a glitter lip! The options are ENDLESS(:

*Keratin treatment/ Keratin  blow-out* 
This service is the most innovative and effective professional smoothing treatment in the world. Through the use of a proprietary keratin-based formulation, the Keratin treatment/keratin blow-Out actually improves the condition of the hair by creating a protective protein layer around the hair shaft to eliminate frizz and smooth the cuticle.
